data.description:
This 4 bed/3.5 bath home in Sunridge Two offers the ultimate convenience with walking distance to over 800 acres of Boulder County open space, King Soopers, local eateries and shops. Step inside one of the larger floor plans in the community to find a welcoming open great room with updated floors, vaulted ceilings, and a cozy fireplace. Natural light floods the space through large windows.

The kitchen boasts a breakfast bar and opens to a spacious formal dining area with access to the backyard. Upstairs, discover generously sized bedrooms, including a primary suite with vaulted ceilings and a private 5 piece ensuite bathroom. The fully finished basement adds extra living space, while the low-maintenance yard with a deck provides a perfect spot to enjoy the Colorado sunshine. Other notable features include a recently replaced roof with a 40-year warranty, fresh paint, upgraded flooring, recently upgraded furnace and central air conditioning, an attached insulated 2-car garage with overhead storage, a fenced yard, cul-de-sac setting, and low HOA fees. With easy highway access and proximity to Denver, Boulder, and Northwest Parkway, this home offers the ideal combination of comfort and convenience.
